      "text": "（麻奈は、東京レイーズでのライブを見事成功させた）",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（俺は麻奈の体調を心配して、ライブの実施に）\n（反対していたが、幸いにも杞憂に終わった）",
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（それでも、麻奈の健康を考えて）\n（一週間の休暇を取ることにしたのだが――）",
      "startTime": 14.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-11.m4a",
      "text": "レイーズのライブ、本当に盛り上がったよね！",
      "startTime": 17.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-05.m4a",
      "text": "今までで最高の出来だったんじゃない？",
      "startTime": 21.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、とても良かったよ。さすがだな",
      "startTime": 24.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん、私を誰だと思ってるの",
      "startTime": 28.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……長瀬麻奈、だろ？",
      "startTime": 32.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-07.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだぞ！　凄いんだぞ！",
      "startTime": 34.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい。だから当然ってことだな\n観客動員記録も更新出来たし、良かったな",
      "startTime": 40.9,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}